highlights.headline: Colby Thomas hits his first career MLB homer
highlights.description: Colby Thomas gives the Athletics an early lead with his first career home run vs. the Nationals.

tracking.trackingName: MLB_One-Play (Colby Thomas hits his first career MLB homer) 2025/08/07 ESHEET

highlights.headline: A's take down Nationals in big win
highlights.description: The Athletics overpower the Nationals in a 6-0 win courtesy of Colby Thomas' first MLB home run, as well as Tyler Soderstrom's two-run dinger.

tracking.trackingName: COM_MLB Highlight (A's take down Nationals in big win) 2025/08/07 ESHEET SOTFULL

headlines.description: — Jacob Lopez struck out a career-high 10 batters in 7 2/3 innings, Colby Thomas hit his first major league home run and drove in three, and the Athletics defeated the Washington Nationals 6-0 on Thursday.
headlines.shortLinkText: Jacob Lopez strikes out career-high 10 in 7 2/3 innings as A's beat the Nationals 6-0

events.name: Chicago White Sox at Seattle Mariners

highlights.headline: Mariners top White Sox in 11 innings
highlights.description: Dominic Canzone's walk-off single proves to be the difference in the Mariner's 4-3 win over the White Sox.

tracking.trackingName: MLB_One-Play (Mariners top White Sox in 11 innings) 2025/08/07 ESHEET

headlines.description: — Dominic Canzone singled home the winning run in the 11th inning and the Seattle Mariners completed a three-game sweep of the Chicago White Sox with a 4-3 victory Thursday.
headlines.shortLinkText: Canzone hits walk-off single in 11th and Mariners top White Sox 4-3 for 3-game sweep

video.headline: Mariners top White Sox in 11 innings

highlights.headline: Paul Skenes, Pirates blank Reds
highlights.description: Paul Skenes finishes with eight strikeouts, and the Pirates get two home runs in a 7-0 win over the Reds.

tracking.trackingName: MLB_One-Play (Paul Skenes, Pirates blank Reds) 2025/08/07 ESHEET

headlines.description: — Paul Skenes struck out eight in six shutout innings, Bryan Reynolds and Henry Davis homered and the Pittsburgh Pirates defeated the Cincinnati Reds 7-0 on Thursday night.
headlines.shortLinkText: Skenes strikes out 8 in 6 shutout innings as Pirates beat Reds 7-0

highlights.headline: Braves rally past Marlins
highlights.description: The Braves score six unanswered runs to defeat the Marlins 8-6.

headlines.description: — Drake Baldwin homered twice and drove in five runs, Marcell Ozuna also went deep and the Atlanta Braves rallied past the Miami Marlins 8-6 on Thursday night.
headlines.shortLinkText: Baldwin and Ozuna power Braves to 8-6 comeback win over Marlins
